description: Try our easy to follow Tuna And Corn Toasted Rolls recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Tuna And Corn Toasted Rolls Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 20 slices sandwich bread, removing the crusts if wished

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 200Â°C (fan assisted). Line baking trays with baking paper.
In a bowl mix together Heinz Seriously Good Mayonnaise and dried French onion soup mix. Stir in drained Greenseas Tuna Chunks and the drained Golden Circle Corn Kernels.
Spread one side of each slice of bread with butter. Spread tuna mix on unbuttered side. Roll up tightly. Place join side down on the prepared trays.
Bake for 15-20 minutes until golden and crisp. Allow to cool for a few minutes before serving
